{"tid":581141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[哭訴]港人去年曾遇生活壓力事件　女士又比男士多","createTime":"2018-03-05T05:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T05:51:05.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c399c707d3d217403e9597f46822062e25ec08ae","tid":581141,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"有調查發現，超過一半的香港人在過去一年，曾經歷一次或以上的生活壓力事件，而女士比男士有較多生活壓力事件，令女士的生活滿意程度下降。 港大醫學院精神學系委託港大民意研究計劃團隊，今年1至2月以電話形式訪問了1514名市民，就生活壓力及生活滿意程度進行調查。 結果發現男女的生活壓力事件，主要來自工作或學業壓力、健康和家庭或感情等。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">女士比男士多生活壓力事件，因此令女士的生活滿意度下降，從而隱藏自己的精神健康狀況。</span></span> 另外，調查亦發現年紀越大，生活滿意程度越高。"},{"pid":"a1aef409fd68f631a39ccc48642d77ce8e70db7d","tid":581141,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b811d75607ca621a8c381591af6957c487793dd","tid":581141,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e08de6b8f86ed0978c1cf0c921209781d13e407","tid":581141,"uid":57554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/134339_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F134339_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=674e4db8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7851cabd74c52c7411ec6060952f8e71feede2cc","tid":581141,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ed4ac487808ef490df0731c2548e421a29ba92","tid":581141,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"女權推左咁耐<img src=\"/ass